name: Nikhil Rajpal
title: Enterprise Account Executive | MBA Candidate
summary: Results-driven Enterprise Account Executive with over 8 years of experience in SaaS, enterprise technology, and CRM-driven sales environments. Proven expertise in building high-performing teams, driving strategic partnerships, and exceeding targets in competitive markets. Currently pursuing an MBA at Leeds University Business School to strengthen strategic leadership and global business acumen.

experience.description: Leading a team of 6 sales representatives with consistent 100%+ target achievement across 8 quarters. Managing enterprise clients across telecom and fintech verticals, generating multimillion-dollar pipelines and influencing strategic decisions through CXO-level relationships.

Generated $1.1M pipeline and closed $200K in new business through targeted outbound prospecting. Awarded MVP in March 2022 for highest regional pipeline generation and designed multi-channel outreach strategies.
Achieved 120% of quarterly targets and closed 15 new accounts contributing $60K ARR. Spearheaded process improvements for conversion efficiency and delivered product training to new hires.
Delivered risk modelling and catastrophe exposure analysis for global reinsurance clients. Collaborated with senior underwriters to assess high-value risks and mentored junior analysts.
